---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import SocialIcons from '../components/SocialIcons.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="About Josh Ferrara — product strategist, dad, musician, reader, photographer."
>
  <header class="about-header">
    <img src="/images/josh.jpg" alt="Josh Ferrara" class="about-photo" width="100" height="100" />
    <h1>About</h1>
  </header>

  <div class="prose">
    <p class="lede">
      I'm Josh Ferrara — a product strategist in Baton Rouge, Louisiana. I spend
      my days thinking about how software gets made, and how the tools we build
      shape the way people live and work.
    </p>

    <h2>A little context</h2>
    <p>
      I lead the product solutions practice at Make, a full-cycle software
      studio, where most of my work lives in the space between a rough idea and
      a shipped product — discovery, shaping, and the hundred small decisions in
      between. I care about craft, and about the parts of building software that
      never show up in a changelog: taste, judgment, and knowing which problem
      is actually worth solving.
    </p>
    <p>
      Outside of work, most of my attention goes to my family. The rest gets
      split between music, photography, reading, film, and — lately — an
      unreasonable amount of Formula 1. I've come to think those things aren't a
      distraction from the work so much as the texture that makes it worth
      doing.
    </p>

    <h2>Career</h2>
    <div class="timeline">
      <div class="timeline__item">
        <div class="timeline__date">2019 &ndash; Present</div>
        <div class="timeline__content">
          <h3>Head of Product Solutions</h3>
          <p class="timeline__company">Make (letsMake.com) / Oven Bits</p>
          <p>Leading the product solutions practice for a full-cycle software agency, developing client discovery and delivery processes.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline__item">
        <div class="timeline__date">2017 &ndash; 2019</div>
        <div class="timeline__content">
          <h3>Chief Operating Officer</h3>
          <p class="timeline__company">Sozo Church</p>
          <p>Oversaw the planning, launch, and ongoing operations of an investment-funded startup church in San Francisco.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline__item">
        <div class="timeline__date">2013 &ndash; 2017</div>
        <div class="timeline__content">
          <h3>Director of Digital Product</h3>
          <p class="timeline__company">Gateway Church</p>
          <p>Led a cross-functional department building and deploying technology products for a staff of over 1,500 and a congregation of 100,000+.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline__item">
        <div class="timeline__date">2013 &ndash; 2017</div>
        <div class="timeline__content">
          <h3>Creative / Marketing</h3>
          <p class="timeline__company">Hivemind Creative, LLC</p>
          <p>Co-founded a technology consulting agency supporting small to medium businesses in building their web presence.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline__item">
        <div class="timeline__date">2012 &ndash; 2013</div>
        <div class="timeline__content">
          <h3>Software Engineer</h3>
          <p class="timeline__company">Anedot</p>
          <p>Early stage full-stack engineer in a venture-funded startup building products for political fundraising campaigns.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline__item">
        <div class="timeline__date">2011 &ndash; 2013</div>
        <div class="timeline__content">
          <h3>Co-Founder / Developer</h3>
          <p class="timeline__company">Hivemind Labs</p>
          <p>Account executive and interactive web and mobile application developer, working directly with clients.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="timeline__item">
        <div class="timeline__date">2010 &ndash; 2011</div>
        <div class="timeline__content">
          <h3>Interactive Developer</h3>
          <p class="timeline__company">Gatorworks</p>
          <p>Crafting interactive websites and applications for clients.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2>Background</h2>
    <p>
      I grew up in the South and studied at LSU. I started out building websites
      and interactive projects, drifted into engineering, co-founded a couple of
      small companies, and eventually found my way to product — which turned out
      to be the thing that tied all the earlier detours together. The
      through-line, if there is one, is that I like making things, and I like the
      people I make them with.
    </p>

    <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
    <SocialIcons />
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  .about-photo {
    width: 100px;
    height: 100px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    object-fit: cover;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .prose {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    font-family: var(--font-serif-text);
  }

  .prose > p {
    font-family: var(--font-serif-text);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  .prose h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
  }

  .lede {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-heading);
  }

  /* Timeline */
  .timeline {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
  }

  .timeline__item {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 140px 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .timeline__date {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    padding-top: var(--space-1);
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }

  .timeline__content h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .timeline__company {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .timeline__content p:last-child {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .about-header {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .timeline__item {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-1);
    }
  }
</style>
